subsection.def:
Board
                    (註冊局) means the Social Workers Registration
                Board established under section 4(1);

committee
                    (委員會) means a committee established under
                    section 8(1)(a);

Director
                    (署長) means the Director of Social Welfare and
                includes a representative of the Director;

panel
                    (備選委員小組) means the disciplinary committee
                panel appointed under section 26(1);

Register
                    (註冊紀錄冊) means the register established under
                    section 7(1)(a);

registered
                    (註冊) means registered under this
                Ordinance;

Registrar
                    (註冊主任) means the Registrar appointed under
                    section 15(1);

paragraph.content:
if the person falls within the description of section
                    4A(1)(a)—must not take up the office of a member of the Board;
                    or

has been sentenced to imprisonment, whether suspended or not, by any court
                    or
                    magistrate;

has been found guilty of a disciplinary
                    offence;
                    or

