                        paragraph (b), in respect of which the Board has performed its function
                        under paragraph (c);

paragraph.content:
establish committees to advise the Board on the performance of its
                    functions and the exercise of its powers (including committees which have
                    members who are not members of the Board);

subparagraph.content:
